Instructions on How To Run Xampp

Start xampp 
cd /opt/lampp
Now run xampp with:
sudo ./manager-linux-x64.run

Although you run the above (located in lampp), http://localhost is the htdocs file. S htdocs is the route for the filepath of the php file you wish to open.  

When opened, go to manage servers and start all 

To open a file inside htdocs :
http://localhost/path to file or just filename


